---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Monthly update
description: A plain-English summary of what changed in the latest monthly public finances release, and why.
---
{% from "components/macros.njk" import caveatBox, dataFreshnessBadge %}

{% set u = monthlyUpdates.updates[0] %}

<div class="page-intro prose">
  <h1>Monthly update: {{ u.month }}</h1>
  <p class="lede">{{ u.headline }}</p>
  <p class="updated">Released {{ u.published | readableDate }}. {{ dataFreshnessBadge(u.confidence_level, "") }}</p>
</div>

<section aria-labelledby="borrowing-heading">
  <h2 id="borrowing-heading" class="visually-hidden">Borrowing this month</h2>
  <div class="metric-grid metric-grid--compact">
    <article class="metric-card metric-card--mini"><p class="metric-card__value">£{{ u.borrowing.value }} bn</p><p class="metric-card__label">Borrowed in {{ u.month }} ({{ u.borrowing.direction }})</p></article>
    <article class="metric-card metric-card--mini"><p class="metric-card__value">{{ u.borrowing.vsLastYear }}</p><p class="metric-card__label">Versus the same month last year</p></article>
    <article class="metric-card metric-card--mini"><p class="metric-card__value">{{ u.borrowing.vsForecast }}</p><p class="metric-card__label">Versus the official forecast</p></article>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="prose" aria-labelledby="qa-heading">
  <h2 id="qa-heading">What changed, and why</h2>
  <dl class="def-list">
    <dt>What changed this month?</dt>
    <dd>{{ u.answers.whatChanged }}</dd>
    <dt>Why did borrowing move?</dt>
    <dd>{{ u.answers.borrowingWhy }}</dd>
    <dt>What happened to tax receipts?</dt>
    <dd>{{ u.answers.taxReceipts }}</dd>
    <dt>What happened to spending?</dt>
    <dd>{{ u.answers.spending }}</dd>
    <dt>What happened to debt interest?</dt>
    <dd>{{ u.answers.debtInterest }}</dd>
    <dt>How does this compare with the OBR forecast?</dt>
    <dd>{{ u.answers.vsObr }}</dd>
  </dl>
</section>

<p class="source-note">
  Source: <a href="{{ u.source_url }}" rel="noopener">{{ u.source_name }}</a>.
  Retrieved {{ u.retrieved_date | readableDate }}.
  {{ dataFreshnessBadge(u.confidence_level, "") }}
</p>

{{ caveatBox("One month is a weak guide to the year. Monthly figures are volatile, seasonal, and routinely revised as fuller data arrives. Read the direction, not the decimal.", "A note on monthly figures") }}
